                <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">Promise in ad creative</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-secondary text-sm">Simple problem statement + believable quick win + call-to-action.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-xl border border-[rgb(17,168,255)] p-5 bg-white">
                <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wide text-[rgb(17,168,255)]">Landing Side</p>
                <p class="mt-2 font-semibold">Matching promise on page</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-secondary text-sm">Same language, same claim, same action. Congruence keeps buyer confidence high and your offer clear.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          )}

          {s.variant === 7 && (
            <div class="mt-5 grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
              <div class="lg:col-span-3 rounded-xl border border-separator p-5 bg-[rgb(250,250,250)]">
                <p class="font-semibold">Offer stack for this phase</p>
                <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-secondary text-sm list-disc list-inside">
                  <li>Meta Ads message-to-page congruence blueprint</li>
                  <li>Low-ticket website copy blocks and CTA placement</li>
                  <li>Break-even and follow-up monetization planning sheet</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="lg:col-span-2 rounded-xl border border-separator p-5 bg-white shadow-natural">
                <p class="text-xs text-tertiary uppercase tracking-wide">Pricing Ladder</p>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm">Low-ticket setup: <span class="font-semibold">{lowTicketOffer.price}</span></p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-sm">Implementation sprint: <span class="font-semibold">by scope</span></p>
                <p class="mt-1 text-secondary text-sm">This front-end offer is the entry point to hiring us for full implementation.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          )}

          {s.variant === 8 && (
            <div class="mt-5 rounded-xl border border-separator p-5 bg-[rgb(250,250,250)]">
              <p class="font-semibold">72-hour sprint view</p>
              <div class="mt-3 grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-3">
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-separator bg-white p-3"><p class="text-xs text-tertiary">Day 1</p><p class="font-medium text-sm mt-1">Clarify offer + ad promise</p></div>
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-separator bg-white p-3"><p class="text-xs text-tertiary">Day 2</p><p class="font-medium text-sm mt-1">Build conversion website section flow</p></div>
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-separator bg-white p-3"><p class="text-xs text-tertiary">Day 3</p><p class="font-medium text-sm mt-1">Launch + monitor economics</p></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          )}

          {s.variant === 9 && (
            <div class="mt-5 rounded-xl border border-separator p-5 bg-white shadow-natural">
              <p class="font-semibold">Low-ticket web funnel conversion flywheel</p>
              <div class="mt-3 grid sm:grid-cols-4 gap-2 text-sm">
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-separator p-3 bg-[rgb(250,250,250)]">Meta ad click</div>
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-separator p-3 bg-[rgb(250,250,250)]">Low-ticket purchase</div>
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-separator p-3 bg-[rgb(250,250,250)]">Warm lead nurture</div>
                <div class="rounded-lg border border-[rgb(17,168,255)] p-3 bg-white">Repeat sale or booked call</div>
              </div>
              <p class="mt-3 text-secondary text-sm">This is how your front-end service funds growth and strengthens long-term customer value.</p>
            </div>
          )}

          <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-2.5">
            <a href={primaryCta} class="text-sm btn-primary text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg inline-flex">Hire Us To Build This Section</a>
            <a href={secondaryCta} class="text-sm px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-separator bg-white hover:bg-black/5 inline-flex">Send Me Scope</a>
          </div>
        </section>
      ))}
    </section>

    <section class="mt-8 rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-natural border border-separator p-8 sm:p-10 text-center">
      <p class="text-[rgb(17,168,255)] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-sm">Final CTA</p>
      <h2 class="mt-2 text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Want us to build your low-ticket funnel for paid ad traffic?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-secondary text-base sm:text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        If you want paid traffic that converts with less waste and more certainty, hire us.
        We will build your low-ticket funnel website, align it to your Meta ads, and optimize it for clear, coherent buying decisions.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex justify-center">
        <a href={primaryCta} class="text-sm sm:text-base btn-primary font-semibold text-white px-7 py-3 rounded-xl tracking-[-0.0125em] inline-flex items-center justify-center transition-colors">
          Hire Stackpine Now
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="w-full py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl px-6 mx-auto border-t border-separator pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between gap-4">
      <span class="text-secondary text-sm">Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} Stackpine</span>
      <a href="mailto:support@stackpine.com" class="text-sm font-medium hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity">support@stackpine.com</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
